    title:"Case 1: Sarah",subtitle:"Sedentary Office Worker — Base Training Design",
    scenario:`Sarah, 42, works 8 hours/day at a desk. Recent health screening shows elevated fasting glucose, borderline hypertension, and low cardiorespiratory fitness. She has never exercised regularly. Her goals are to improve health markers and lose weight. She expresses concern about being "too unfit" for group fitness classes.

