    answer:`1) BASE TRAINING: Sarah is inactive with low fitness. Zone 1 (RPE 3–4, below VT1 @ 105 bpm) provides positive experience, low injury risk. No assessments needed at this phase (would only confirm low fitness = discouraging).

2) INITIAL 4-WEEK BLOCK:
• Frequency: 3 days/week (Mon/Wed/Fri)
