• Rationale: Sedentary breaks reduce metabolic risk INDEPENDENT of structured exercise

4) PROGRESSION CRITERIA → Fitness Training:
• Sarah sustains 20+ min continuous Zone 1 comfortably (4–6 weeks typically)
• HR at same pace declining (training effect: VT1 HR adaptation)
