  {
    title:"Case 2: Marcus",subtitle:"Osteoarthritis — Water Exercise Prescription",
    scenario:`Marcus, 67, has osteoarthritis in both knees and hips. He stopped exercising at 60 due to joint pain with land-based activity. Recent knee arthroscopy did not fully restore function. BMI 29, wants to improve cardiorespiratory fitness.

