    answer:`1) JAVIER QUALIFIES — READINESS CRITERIA MET:
✓ Aerobic base: 45+ min sustained zone 1–2 exercise
✓ VO₂max: 48 mL/kg/min (well-trained recreational level)
✓ RHR 58 bpm (aerobic adaptation confirmed)
